Haɓaka cikin sauri a cikin tarin cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin EU/EEA da UK, tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020
Haɗakar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) na nuna irin wannan ci gaba a ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/Ƙungiyar Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Ƙasar Ingila, yana tabbatar da cewa, ko da yake a matakai daban-daban, cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Daga ƙwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da wuraren kula da marasa lafiya masu tsanani suna buƙatar shirya don ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman na ICU.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu rahoton wani mutum da ya kamu da cutar huhu da ba a san asalinsa ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Kula da Cututtuka ta China ta gano cewa sabon coronavirus da yanzu aka sani da SARS-CoV-2 ne ya haddasa cutar.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 ana kiranta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
A yau, kusan kashi 80 cikin 100 na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya, wato, suna da cutar numfashi tare ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawanci suna warkewa.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin 100 na masu kamuwa da COVID-19, cutar ta kai ga wani mummunan yanayi da ya bukaci a kwantar da su a asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin 100 na masu kamuwa da cutar suka kamu da wani mummunan yanayi da ya bukaci kulawa ta musamman.
Yawan mutanen da ke mutuwa a asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, muna nazarin yanayin da ake samu na tarin kamuwa da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin Ƙungiyar Tarayyar Turai/Ƙungiyar Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da kuma a Ƙasar Ingila (UK), muna kwatanta shi da yanayin da aka samu a lardin Hubei na ƙasar Sin.
Muna kuma kwatanta adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da United Kingdom da na Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da kuma UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa, kuma yanayin annobar COVID-19 a sauran duniya a halin yanzu yana bin wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Babban Daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin editan 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbacin COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ma'anar WHO na shari'ar.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ce ta fara samun mutum uku da suka kamu da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano masu COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya (UK), tare da 39,768 da suka kamu da cutar da kuma 1,727 da suka mutu a ranar 31 ga Disamba, ciki har da 17,750 da kuma 1,441 da suka mutu a Italiya kaɗai.
Samun adadin adadin da kuma yawan adadin COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Ƙasashen Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin COVID-19 da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samu daga tushe na hukuma kamar ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki na ƙasashe daban-daban da WHO, kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da kuma UK, da kuma kwatanta da ƙwarewar Italiya.
Don a tantance yawan masu COVID-19 da ke aiki, mun yi lissafin yawan masu COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14, don haka la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a cikin kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da kuma a Burtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin adadin da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe tare da bayanan Italiya na lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da United Kingdom
A cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK, yawanci ana bin yanayin cutar COVID-19 a lardin Hubei (China) a cikin kwanaki 14 (Hotuna 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da United Kingdom, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa ne a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, kuma ya karu sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (ƙarin bayani).
Wannan ya faru ne saboda karuwar da aka samu a cikin sauri a cikin Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da United Kingdom sun sami irin wannan ƙaruwa a cikin adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 (ƙarin bayani).
Hoto 2 ya nuna adadin adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma United Kingdom a kan bayanan Italiya na 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
An gano cewa a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma United Kingdom sun riga sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin da ya yi daidai da na Italiya da ke da makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin rahoton COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Ƙarin yawan masu kamuwa da COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar tana ci gaba da sauri a ƙasashe duka.
Wannan ya faru duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban kuma akwai bambance-bambance a cikin martanin da hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa suka bayar, da yiwuwar bambance-bambance a cikin ma'anar cutar da bambance-bambance a cikin hanyoyin zaɓan marasa lafiya da za a gwada don tabbatar da COVID-19, ciki har da gwajin sake dawowa.
A farkon Maris 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun ce kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 na marasa lafiyar COVID-19 suna bukatar kulawa ta musamman, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da wuraren kula da marasa lafiya a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun cika.
Bayanai game da shigar da COVID-19 a asibiti da/ko ICU a halin yanzu ana samun su a cikin EU/EEA don kawai kashi 6 da 1% na masu kamuwa da cutar, bi da bi (ba a bayar da bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, ana bukatar tattara bayanai a kai a kai don a cika bayanan da ake da su na lura da cutar, wanda ya ta'allaka ne kan yawan mutanen da aka kamu da su da kuma waɗanda suka mutu.
Binciken da aka yi a 201011 ya nuna cewa akwai bambanci sosai a yawan gadaje da ake samu a cibiyoyin kulawa da ke tsakiya da na musamman a Turai, daga gadaje 29.2 ga kowane mutum 100,000 a Jamus zuwa gadaje 4.2 a Portugal.
Hakan na nufin cewa ƙasashen suna da ƙarin ko ƙasa da na Italiya (12.5 na ICU da matsakaiciyar gado a kowace mutum 100,000 a shekara ta 2010-11).
An samar da yanayin yanayin da ya shafi yawan kulawa, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da kuma UK na yawan COVID-19 da ke cikin asibiti tare da haɗarin &gt; kashi 90 cikin ɗari na wucewa na gado a cikin ICU, a cikin sabuntawa ta shida na COVID-19 Rapid Risk Assessment na CEPCM.
Saboda an tattara lamura zuwa yanzu a wasu yankuna na EU/EEA da United Kingdom, kuma asibitoci da ICU suna daukar wasu yankuna, ya kamata a tattara bayanai na lamura da ICU gado a matakin 2 na Nomenclature of Territorial Statistical Units (NUTS 2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma ci gaban da ake samu a sauran ƙasashe ya nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da kuma wuraren kula da marasa lafiya masu tsanani dole su shirya don yanayin da za a iya samun ƙarin masu ɗauke da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma ƙaruwa a yawan marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19 da ke bukatar kulawa, musamman ma a wuraren kula da marasa lafiya masu tsanani, kamar yadda aka gani a yankunan Italiya da cutar ta shafa.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sabon saurin tantance haɗarin da ECDC ta yi, hanzarin, da hanzarin da kuma cikakken tsarin na da muhimmanci wajen rage yaduwar SARS-COV-2, daga hanyar da za a bi don a rage, domin saurin da kuma farkon karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar zai iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, yarda da kuma daidaita yadda suke amsawa idan ba a yi wani abu ba.
Binciken haɗarin cikin sauri ya kuma nuna matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokaci wanda kowace ƙasa za ta iya ƙara ƙoƙarin sarrafawa don rage saurin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba a kan ayyukan kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba haka ba, akwai yiwuwar tsarin kiwon lafiya a sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA zai fuskanci hauhawar yawan marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
