A ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta wallafa wata shawara mai sauri don gano da kuma magance cutar coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV) kuma wannan shawara ta bayyana kwarewarmu da kuma bayar da shawarwari don yaƙi da wannan annoba a duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) sabon abu ne, iliminmu da iliminmu suna ci gaba a hankali bisa ga sakamakon binciken da ake gudanarwa da kuma kwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, dabarun bincike da magani ana sabunta su koyaushe.
A cikin wannan wasikar, mun amsa wata sanarwa game da ƙa'idodinmu kuma mun ba da sabon tsarin bincike don  wanda ake zargi  da  wanda aka tabbatar  bisa ga sabon tsarin bincike da magani na COVID-19 (juzu'i na bakwai) wanda Hukumar Lafiya ta Ƙasa ta Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ta buga.
A watan Disambar 2019, sabon coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da cutar da yanzu an kira shi cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), kuma an sanya wa kwayar cutar suna coronavirus 2 mai saurin numfashi (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, WHO ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
