Asalin kwayar cutar ta mutum
Cutar cututtukan cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) da cutar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) sun nuna yadda cutar HCoV za ta iya zama mai haɗari da kuma kisa.
Yawancin HCoVs suna fitowa ne daga jemage, wanda ba su da ƙwayoyin cuta.
An yi amfani da maganin maganin maganin rigakafi na HCoV-235 a cikin maganin rigakafin cutar HIV na farko.
Gano dabbobi masu shayarwa yana da tasiri kai tsaye a cikin rigakafin cutar ɗan adam.
Binciken hulɗar CoV-mai watsawa a cikin dabbobi na iya taimakawa wajen fahimtar CoV a cikin mutane.
An rarraba CoVs zuwa jinsuna huɗu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV, da delta-CoV) bisa ga bambancin jerin sunayen sunadarai. Nau'in Beta-CoV yana ƙunshe da yawancin HCoVs kuma an rarraba shi zuwa jinsuna huɗu (A, B, C, da D).
Bayanai na phylogenetic ya nuna cewa jemagu da rodents suna aiki a matsayin tushen kwayar halittar ga mafi yawan alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye sune babban wurin ajiye gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
A yau, an san CoVs na mutum bakwai (HCoVs).
HCoV-NL63 da HCoV-229E sune alpha-CoVs, wanda ke nuna alamun cutar.
Sauran beta-CoV guda biyar sun haɗa da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, SARS-CoV, Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS-CoV) da kuma SARS-CoV-2.
Bincike kan asalin halittar HCoV na dabba ya ba da tsari don fahimtar tarihin halitta, abubuwan motsawa da kuma abubuwan da ke hana ƙetare shingen nau'in.
Hakanan zai iya jagorantar ko sauƙaƙa bincike don mai masauki, matsakaici da mai ƙarfafa SARS-CoV-2, tare da mahimmancin tasiri a cikin rigakafin kamuwa da cuta a nan gaba.
An san CoVs na dabbobi tun daga ƙarshen shekarun 1930s.
A cikin shekarun da suka gabata, an gano HCoVs bakwai.
An ware nau'in HCoV-229E na farko daga hanyoyin numfashi na marasa lafiya da ke da cututtukan sama na numfashi a 1966, daga baya ya daidaita don girma a cikin kwayoyin WI-38.
Marasa lafiyar da ke dauke da HCoV-229E suna da alamun sanyi na yau da kullum, wanda ya haɗa da ciwon kai, yin atishawa, rashin jin daɗi da ciwon makogwaro, tare da zazzabi da tari a kashi 10 zuwa 20 na masu kamuwa.
HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 suna nan a ko'ina a duniya kuma ana ganin ana yaɗuwa ne a lokacin hunturu, a ƙasashe masu yanayi mai laushi.
Shagunan Australiya sun rage adadin takardar bayan gida da za su saya
A daren Lahadi da Asabar, shagunan Woolworths da Coles na Australia sun rage takunkumin sayen takardar bayan gida zuwa biyu da kuma kunshin sayayya guda a duk shaguna a duk fadin kasar, bi da bi.
A ranar Litinin, ALDI ta kuma sanya wa'adin da za a iya amfani da shi a cikin kaya guda.
An sanya waɗannan iyakokin a matsayin saƙonni a wuraren biya da kuma shafukan Facebook na tashoshin.
Masu sayen sun yi ajiyar kayayyaki saboda tsoron COVID-19 da kuma bukatar a yi wa mutane allurar rigakafin.
A ranar Laraba, Woolworths ya kuma takaita sayen takarda bayan gida zuwa kunshin daya.
Waɗannan matakan sun biyo bayan ƙuntatawa na kunshin huɗu da Woolworths da Coles suka gabatar a ranar 4 da 5 ga Maris, bi da bi.
Coles, a cikin sanarwar da ya fitar a ranar 8 ga Maris, ya ce tare da ƙuntatawa na kunshin huɗu da ke aiki, yawancin shaguna har yanzu suna cikin aji a cikin awa ɗaya bayan isarwa, kuma ya kira buƙatar "maras kyau", yayin da ALDI, a cikin post na Facebook na ranar Talata, ya kira shi "ba zato ba tsammani".
An samu karuwar tallace-tallace a makon da ya gabata, a cewar mai magana da yawun Woolworths.
Shagon Costco a Canberra ya kuma rage adadin da ake ba da izinin cin abinci zuwa fakiti biyu a makon da ya gabata.
Don rage ƙarancin, Coles ya ba da umarnin manyan kunshe daga masu kaya kuma ya ƙara yawan isar da su, Woolworths ya ba da umarnin ƙarin kaya, yayin da ALDI ya ba da kaya da wuri don ingantawa a ranar Laraba.
Russell Zimmerman, babban daraktan kungiyar 'yan kasuwar Ostiraliya, ya ce 'yan kasuwar suna kokarin tara kayayyaki, amma dokar da aka kafa ta majalisar dokokin yankin ta hana a kai kaya ta hanyar manyan motoci.
Ya ce farashin kayayyaki zai ƙaru yayin da masu samar da kayayyaki za su yi ƙoƙari su biya bukatar da ake da su, kuma za a rage tallace-tallace.
A ranar Talata, ALDI ta sanar da cewa bayan an fara fitar da kayayyaki, wasu shaguna ba za su iya biyan kuɗin tallafin na ranar Laraba ba.
A cikin wani labarin da News.com.au ya wallafa, Dr. Gary Mortimer, masanin masana'antun sayar da kayayyaki a jami'ar Queensland University of Technology, ya ce shagunan suna cika kayayyaki a kowane dare.
Ya ce takardar bayan wanki babban kaya ne, wanda ke haifar da karancin kayayyaki, wanda idan aka gama, sai ya bar manyan wuraren da ba a ajiye su ba, wanda ke ƙara nuna ƙarancin kayayyaki.
"Coles da Woolworths suna ganin [idan] ɗakunan ajiya sun cika, idan za a iya sayen kayayyaki kamar na'urar wanki da na'urar kashe ƙwayoyi kuma ana samunsu da yawa, hakan zai iya rage fargabar", in ji Russell Zimmerman a ABC News.
Kamfanin da ke kera takardun bayan gida da ake amfani da su a baya ya ce ba su da kayayyaki.
Kimberly-Clark, wanda ke kera takardar wanki Kleenex, da Solaris Paper wanda ke kera takardar Sorbent, sun jaddada cewa suna aiki 24/7 don kiyaye wadata, a cewar News.com.au.
Shafin mallakar ƙasa Domain.com ya ba da rahoton cewa wasu masu sayar da ƙasa suna ba da takardar bayan gida kyauta ga mai sayarwa na farko a Melbourne yayin da aka rage yawan sayarwa saboda masu siye suna hutu a ƙarshen ƙarshen ranar aiki.
A ranar Alhamis ne aka buga jaridar NT News, wadda a kullum ake buga ta a Darwin, kuma ta ƙunshi shafi takwas da za a yanka su a yi amfani da su a matsayin takardar shara.
Shagunan sun kasance masu ƙin saka takunkumi, a cewar wani rahoto na ranar 3 ga Maris daga ABC Australia inda suka sanar cewa ba su da shirin saka takunkumin sayayya.
Russell Zimmerman ya kara da cewa wasu kayayyaki ma suna cikin bukatar, kamar su abin rufe fuska, magungunan kashe ƙwari, kayan bushewa, kayan wanke hannu da kuma gari.
